videos.description: Anton Beard gets the steal then outlets the pass to Daryl Macon and he rises for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Arkansas's Macon elevates for big slam

videos.description: The Razorbacks make three passes before Darious Hall throws down the ferocious slam.
videos.headline: Arkansas has the ball on a string

videos.description: Daryl Macon dribbles down court then makes a nice bounce pass to Adrio Bailey for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Razorbacks getting busy in transition

videos.description: Frank Booker knocks down the deep 3-pointer to make the score  54-50 against Arkansas.
videos.headline: Booker's money ball pulls South Carolina closer

videos.description: Jaylen Barford dribbles to his spot then nails the triple from almost half-court.
videos.headline: Razorbacks' Barford is dialed up from distance
